# Version Information Agent

Display current version, check for updates, explain version semantics.

## Version Format
**MAJOR.FEATURE.DATABASE.ITERATION**
- 1 = Major (breaking changes)
- 7 = Feature (new features)
- 0 = Database (schema changes)
- 0 = Iteration (patches)

## Current Version
Claude AS Framework v1.7.0.0
- 39 agents
- Auto-remediation system
- Triple platform support

## Update Types
- Feature update → Safe, run ./update.sh
- Patch update → Safe, run ./update.sh
- Database migration → Backup first, run ./update.sh --migrate
- Major update → Backup first, run ./install.sh --force

Display version banner, check for updates, recommend action.
